---
import "../styles/cta.scss";
import Link from "./Link.astro";
---

<section>
    <h2>About me</h2>
    <p id="about_me" class="grid">
        <img
            style="max-width: 150px; padding-left: 0"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="grid__item"
            src="/img/old-laptop.webp"
            alt="old laptop computer"
        />
        <span class="grid__item" style="padding:0!important">
            <b>Low-end hardware? Not a problem!</b>
            My software is well optimised and runs on almost any device. Including
            old laptop from the early 2000s without an internet connection.
        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="height: 4rem"></p>
    <p id="about_me" class="grid">
        <img
            style="max-width: 150px; padding-left: 0"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="grid__item"
            src="/img/servers.webp"
            alt="servers"
        />
        <span class="grid__item" style="padding:0!important">
            <b>Distributed systems? I got you covered!</b>
            From monoliths to microservices, from single machines to server farms.
            I have experience with all of them and will ensure that your project
            has the right scale.
        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="height: 4rem"></p>
    <p>
        I love working with startups or mid-sized companies with ambitious
        goals.
    </p>
    <p>
        As a <b>Software Engineer</b> I plan your software project and make sure
        that you get the best results possible.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
        I am a well organised problem solver with <b
            >high attention to the detail</b
        > and a passion for <b>good architecture</b>.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
        In my free time I watch anime, play video games and listen to jazz and
        rock music.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p><b>Let's get together and create the next great app.</b></p>
    <br />
    <h2>Tools I use</h2>
    <p class="flex-list">
        <Link href="https://neovim.io/">
            <img
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                style="height: 2em"
                alt=""
                src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3a/Neovim-mark.svg"
            />
            Neovim
        </Link>
        <Link href="https://github.com/wez/wezterm">
            <img
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                style="height: 2em"
                alt=""
                src="https://wezfurlong.org/wezterm/favicon.svg"
            />
            WezTerm
        </Link>
        <Link href="https://arc.net/">
            <img
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                style="height: 2em"
                alt="arc icon"
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Frank-Mayer/Frank-Mayer/master/img/arc.svg"
            />
            Arc
        </Link>
        <Link href="https://www.figma.com/">
            <img
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                style="height: 2em"
                alt="figma icon"
                src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/33/Figma-logo.svg"
            />
            Figma
        </Link>
    </p>
</section>
